# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok cambridge - jury selection began tuesday in the child rape trial of former catholic priest paul r. shanley as prospective jurors were questioned about the clergy abuse scandal and their exposure to pretrial publicity .
# ::alignments
(b / begin-01
      :ARG1 (s / select-01
            :ARG1 (j / jury))
      :ARG2 (t / try-02
            :ARG1 (p / priest
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Paul"
                        :op2 "R."
                        :op3 "Shanley")
                  :mod (r / religious-group
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Catholic"))
                  :time (f / former))
            :ARG3 (r2 / rape-01
                  :ARG1 (c / child)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / tuesday))
      :time (q / question-01
            :ARG1 (a / and
                  :op1 (s2 / scandal
                        :topic (a2 / abuse-01
                              :ARG1 (c2 / clergy)))
                  :op2 (e / expose-01
                        :ARG1 (j2 / jur
                              :ARG2 (p2 / publicity
                                    :mod (p3 / pretrial))))
                  :ARG2 (j3 / jurist
                        :mod (p4 / prospective)))
            :location (c3 / city
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Cambridge"))))

                  :ARG0 (s2 / shut-down-05
                        :ARG1 (f / factory
                              :quant 3
                              :mod (a / all)
                              :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                                    :ARG2 (f2 / factory
                                          :mod (m2 / main)
                                          :poss c))))
                  :ARG1 (h2 / have-03
                        :polarity -
                        :ARG0 (p3 / population
                              :quant (m3 / much))
                        :ARG1 (ii2 / income
                              :mod (a2 / any))
                        :duration (m4 / multiple

                                    :quant 1
                                    :unit (m5 / month))))))

            :weekday (t4 / thursday)))

# ::alignments
(w / work-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Mel"
                  :op2 "Karmazin")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / company
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Sirius"
                              :op2 "XM"))
                  :ARG2 (e / executive
                        :mod (c2 / chief)
                        :mod (ii / irrepressible))))
      :ARG1 (p2 / phone
            :poss p)
      :time (w2 / week
            :mod (l / last))
      :source (o / office
            :mod (c3 / corner)
            :location (f / floor
                  :ord (o2 / ordinal-entity
                        :value "-1")
                  :part-of (b / building
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "McGraw-Hill"))
                  :location (a / above
                        :op1 (s / studio
                              :poss (p3 / person
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Howard"
                                          :op2 " stern")))
                        :mod (j / just)))
            :poss p))

      :ARG1 (p / price-01

      :ARG0-of (a / affect-01
            :ARG1 (o / or
                  :op1 (m / market
                        :mod (w / whole))
                  :op2 (m2 / market
                        :quant (s3 / series))))
      :domain (c / crash-01
            :ARG1 (m3 / market
                  :mod (s4 / stock))))
